					</div><!-- /col-lg-6 -->
					
				</div><!-- /row -->
			</div><!-- /container -->
		</div><!-- /headerwrap -->
		
		
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row mt centered">
				<div class="col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-3">
					<h1>Observe Your Growth As a Professional</h1>
					<h3>Stop trying to remember accomplishments and wins right before performance reviews. Understand and monitor your professional and personal progress through regular journal entries</h3>
				</div>
			</div><!-- /row -->
			
			<div class="row mt centered">
				<div class="col-lg-4">
					<img src="<%= image_path("briefcase.png") %>" width="180" alt="">
					<h2>1 - Get Shit Done</h2>
					<h4>This one is all you! Make moves, take risks, learn somthing. Whatever you're doing, do it well!</h4>
				</div><!--/col-lg-4 -->

				<div class="col-lg-4">
					<img src="<%= image_path("email.png") %>" width="180" alt="">
					<h2>2 - Send Your Thoughts</h2>
					<h4>Whenever you feel like it, send a quick email to 'app_name' about what you're up to. Don't worry if you forget, we'll remind you if you're slacking.</h4>

				</div><!--/col-lg-4 -->

				<div class="col-lg-4">
					<img src="<%= image_path("trends.png") %>" width="180" alt="">
					<h2>3 - Review Your Progress</h2>
					<h4>After some time, you'll have enough entries to really see what you've been up to and evaluate if you're really acheiving your goals!</h4>

				</div><!--/col-lg-4 -->
			</div><!-- /row -->
		</div><!-- /container -->
		
